title: ETERNALS FINAL TRAILER REACTION!! (Marvel Studios' | Breakdown | Celestials)
author: The Reel Rejects
description:
THE FINAL TRAILER FOR ETERNALS HAS ARRIVED! Here's our REACTION & BREAKDOWN featuring up-close looks at Thena (Angelina Jolie), Ajak (Salma Hayek), Sersi (Gemma Chan), Dane Whitman (Black Knight | Kit Harrington), Ikaris (Richard Madden), Kingo (Kumail Nanjiani), Phastos (Brian Tyree Henry), Druig (Barry Keoghan), Makkari (Lauren Ridloff), Gilgamesh (Ma Dong-seok), & Sprite (Lia McHugh) with special guest Coy Jandreau (Comic Book Shopping). Let's go Chloe Zhao!
#Eternals #Marvel #MCU
